(# Transport Reliability and Delay Analytics API) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Overview) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This API manages a curated transport network and records operational incidents such as) Tj
T*
(delays,) Tj
T*
(cancellations, weather disruption, staff shortages, and signalling issues. It is designed) Tj
T*
(for) Tj
T*
(coursework assessment with a focus on realistic domain modelling, analytics, testing, and) Tj
T*
(explainable engineering decisions.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Base URL when running locally:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- http://127.0.0.1:8000) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(API prefix:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- /api/v1) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Authentication) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Protected write endpoints use the `X-API-Key` header.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Admin key: full write access to stations, routes, and incidents) Tj
T*
(- Operator key: create and update incidents only) Tj
T*
(- Public users: read-only access to GET endpoints) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Example header:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(X-API-Key: changeme-admin-key) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Status Codes) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- 200 OK: successful read or update) Tj
T*
(- 201 Created: resource created) Tj
T*
(- 204 No Content: resource deleted) Tj
T*
(- 400 Bad Request: invalid query logic or invalid route/station combination) Tj
T*
(- 401 Unauthorized: missing or invalid API key) Tj
T*
(- 403 Forbidden: authenticated but insufficient role) Tj
T*
(- 404 Not Found: resource does not exist) Tj
T*
(- 409 Conflict: duplicate data or delete blocked by references) Tj
T*
(- 422 Unprocessable Entity: validation failure) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Utility Endpoint) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(GET /health) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Returns a simple readiness payload) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
endobj
