() Tj
T*
(Returns:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- incident_count) Tj
T*
(- average_delay_minutes) Tj
T*
(- cancellation_count) Tj
T*
(- severe_incident_count) Tj
T*
(- reliability_score) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Reliability score is a documented heuristic:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- type weight + severity weight + capped delay contribution per incident) Tj
T*
(- penalties are averaged across the selected time window) Tj
T*
(- score is clamped between 0 and 100) Tj
T*
(- this is an incident-based comparative metric, not an official operator KPI) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(GET /api/v1/analytics/routes/{route_id}/worst-time) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Returns the hour of day with the highest disruption score for a route.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(GET /api/v1/analytics/stations/top-delayed) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Query params: limit, from, to) Tj
T*
(- Returns stations ranked by total delay minutes and incident count) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(GET /api/v1/analytics/incidents/by-hour) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Query params: from, to) Tj
T*
(- Returns incident volume and average delay grouped by hour of day) Tj
T*
() Tj
